title: An integrated carbonized wood-based gas-diffusion electrode for high-current-density CO electrosynthesis in flow cells
content:
Sustainable Energy Fuels, 2024, 8,1641-1649
DOI: 10.1039/D4SE00018H, Paper
Huanhuan Tao, Huaiyu Chang, Fang Wang, Zhengguo Zhang, Shixiong Min
An integrated carbonized wood-based gas-diffusion electrode embedded with reconstructed Ag nanoparticles is developed, exhibiting activity and selectivity towards the CO2RR.
